{"tid":2401624,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣成功獲美國出口500萬劑莫德納疫苗 至今已採購近2000萬劑疫苗","createTime":"2021-02-10T01:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T07:21:48.000Z","uid":292499,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"69bcb31333559a45bdc6fe54336a9f53fdcdadb7","tid":2401624,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:19:45.000Z","msg":"路透報導，美國製藥廠莫德納9日表示，已經和台灣和哥倫比亞政府簽訂疫苗供應協定，分別將提供500萬劑和1000萬劑疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n莫德納在聲明中表示，「莫德納疫苗目前在台灣和哥倫比亞尚未被批准使用，本公司將與其監管機關合作，確保疫苗施打前通過核准」。莫德納指出，將於2021年年中開始運送疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">莫德納疫苗有效率94.5％，保護率破94％，比輝瑞疫苗更高，而上月莫德納更公布好消息，稱實驗室研究指出，莫德納疫苗對英國、南非變種病毒都有保護力。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121475/5245716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121475%2F5245716&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=68122ada\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121475/5245716</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102105003.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202102105003.aspx&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=6c82abb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102105003.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3437340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3437340&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=e3322339\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3437340&h=471b47b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3437340</a>"},{"pid":"9f726b7c62030fa900a74112808959ae865c69d9","t